PTT Global Chemical Appoints Veerasak as New CEO From Today

-- B y   S u t t i n e e   Y u v e j w a t t a n a
-- 
2011-10-19T11:20:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/ptt-global-chemical-appoints-veerasak-as-new-ceo-from-today.html
PTT Global Chemical Pcl said today
its board has appointed Veerasak Kositpaisal as chief executive
officer, according to an e-mailed statement.  PTT Chemical Pcl (PTTCH)  and  PTT Aromatics & Refining Pcl (PTTAR)  are
merging to form PTT Global Chemical.  To contact the reporter on this story:
